Title: Amazing Happiness with Local Citizen
DateModified: '2019-02-15'
DatePublished: '2019-02-15'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/amazing-happiness-with-local-citizen
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Fevtri Sulistiyaningsih
AuthorCountry: Indonesia
Text: Every single moment of our trip is amazing. Especially, in a Country that we
  are never come before. And for me, one of amazing Happiness in every trip is about
  a Local Connection with amazing Local Citizen. All diferences between backpackers
  and Local Citizen is a beatuifull moment when we can talk, telling a story and share
  our happiness. So, that's why I choose "Making a Local Connection" theme for my
  story.
